data.description: Great opportunity to own a single-story home in Goose Creek with NO HOA!  This home features 3 bedrooms and two bathrooms and has NEW flooring throughout. The open concept split floor plan offers privacy for the owner's suite while still giving you the open feel for shared spaces. You'll enjoy the large backyard with plenty of storage for a boat, large garden or children's dream playground.  Endless possibilities! This home is convenient to shopping, restaurants, schools and a fantastic recreation center.  Schedule your showing today.
